data.description:
Enjoy this beautiful Lorain Colonial located just minutes from Lakeview Park with a glimpse of Lake Erie from your
newly updated porch. This home features three bedrooms but has the potential to make four with a very spacious
attic! The backyard is ready for relaxing fall nights by the fire which includes a fenced in area (installed 2021) and a
swing set! Enjoy the many updates this home offers such as a new garage (2021), new windows (2021), attic and wall
insulation (2018)! The charming century home is awaiting your finishing touches just before the holidays!
